---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Ariff Mohamed - Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | MIT Cybersecurity Student"
  description="Expert Azure cloud solutions engineer specializing in security, automation, and compliance. Showcasing enterprise Azure projects including PowerShell automation, KQL analytics, storage security, and Intune device management."
>
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section gradient-primary text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-5xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); color: white; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--line-height-tight);">Ariff Mohamed</h1>
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | Security Specialist</h2>
        <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);">Transforming enterprise cloud infrastructure with security-first Azure architecture and innovative automation solutions. Currently advancing cybersecurity expertise at MIT.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl);">
          <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Azure Projects</a>
          <a href="#about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Azure Projects -->
  <section class="section" id="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); color: var(--text-primary);">Featured Azure Projects</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-8" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);">Explore my specialized Azure implementations focused on automation, security, and enterprise management</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Azure Automation Hub</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description mb-4">Comprehensive PowerShell runbook automation platform for enterprise user management, resource provisioning, and operational workflows. Features advanced scheduling, error handling, and audit trails.</p>
            <a href="https://automation.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore Automation →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Log Analytics Toolkit</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description mb-4">Advanced KQL query library and monitoring dashboard suite for Azure security insights, performance analysis, and compliance reporting. Real-time alerting and custom workbooks included.</p>
            <a href="https://log.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore Analytics →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Secure Storage Patterns</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description mb-4">Enterprise-grade Azure storage security implementations featuring encryption at rest and in transit, compliance frameworks, access policies, and data governance best practices.</p>
            <a href="https://storage.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore Storage →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Device Compliance Monitor</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description mb-4">Microsoft Intune-powered device management and compliance monitoring solution. Automated policy enforcement, security baselines, and comprehensive reporting for enterprise endpoints.</p>
            <a href="https://compliance.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore Compliance →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Side Projects -->
  <section class="section" id="side-projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); color: var(--text-primary);">Side Projects</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-8" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);">Personal development tools and experimental applications</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="card card-accent">
          <div class="card-header flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Todo Application</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description mb-4">A modern, responsive task management application built with modern web technologies. Features task organization, priority management, and progress tracking.</p>
            <a href="https://todo.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">Try Todo App →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); color: var(--text-primary);">About Me</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">As an Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer specializing in security architecture, I bring deep technical expertise in enterprise cloud infrastructure, automation, and compliance. My experience spans large-scale Azure implementations, security frameworks, and innovative problem-solving for complex business challenges.</p>
          
          <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">Currently advancing my expertise through MIT's Cybersecurity program, I'm passionate about developing secure, scalable Azure solutions that drive business value while maintaining the highest security and compliance standards.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise">
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-2xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold); color: var(--accent-400); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">Azure Specializations</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2" style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Azure Security Architecture
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              PowerShell Automation & Runbooks
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              KQL & Log Analytics
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Microsoft Intune Management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Storage Security & Encryption
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Compliance & Governance
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Identity & Access Management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              DevSecOps Implementation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary); padding: var(--space-sm) 0;">
              <span class="icon-placeholder" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Threat Detection & Response
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-size: var(--font-size-4xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold); color: var(--text-primary);">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p class="mb-8" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);">Interested in collaborating on Azure cloud security solutions or discussing enterprise automation projects? Let's connect.</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <a href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com" class="card text-center" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Email</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description">ariff@aglobaltec.com</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ariff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card text-center" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">LinkedIn</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description">Professional Profile</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card text-center" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="icon-placeholder icon-placeholder-lg" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);"></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">GitHub</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p class="card-description">Technical Portfolio</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl);">
        <a href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
</Layout>
